    <br>

    <hr>

    <h2>üîê Instructor / Admin Login (Prerequisite)</h2>

    <p>Only <b>instructors or admins</b> can create, update, or delete courses.</p>

    <h5>Endpoint</h5>
    <pre><code class="language-swift">POST /auth/login</code></pre>
    <br>

    <h5>Headers</h5>
    <pre><code class="language-http">Content-Type: application/json</code></pre>
    <br>

    <h5>Request Body</h5>
    <pre><code class="language-json">{
  "email": "rahul.instructor@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}</code></pre>
    <br>

    <h5>Success Response (200)</h5>
    <pre><code class="language-json">{
  "token": "INSTRUCTOR_1_TOKEN"
}</code></pre>
    <br>

    <p class="mt-2">
        ‚û°Ô∏è Use this token in the <code>Authorization</code> header for protected course routes.
    </p>

